Elimizdeki Tweet verisini gelecek islemler icin duzenleyelim

BidenTweet<- rownames_to_column(JoeBiden) %>% 
  select(created,favoriteCount,retweetCount)
BidenTweet1<-BidenTweet %>% 
  mutate(etkilesim=(favoriteCount+retweetCount)/2)%>% 
  gather(etkilesim, deger,-created)
attach(JoeBiden)
attach(BidenTweet)

Joe Biden’in Attigi Son 500 tweetin aldigi etkilesime bakalim

ggplot(data=BidenTweet1,mapping = aes(created,deger,color=etkilesim)) + geom_jitter(aes(size=4,alpha=0,25))+ labs(x="",y="",title = "Joe Biden'in Son Attigi 500 Tweet Etkilesimleri")+ theme_minimal(base_size = 12)

Peki Joe Biden Gunun Genellikle Hangi Saatlerinde Tweet Atiyor?

joeBiden_Slim <- JoeBiden %>%
  select(id,text,created)

joeBiden_Slim %>%
  count(hour = hour(with_tz(created, "EST"))) %>%
  mutate(percent = n / sum(n)) %>%
  ggplot(aes(hour, percent, color = hour)) +
  geom_line() +
  labs(x = "Hour of day (EST)",
       y = "% of tweets",
       color = "")

Tweet Temizleme

library(tidytext)

reg <- "([^A-Za-z\\d#@']|'(?![A-Za-z\\d#@]))"
tweet_words <- tweets %>%
  filter(!str_detect(text, '^"')) %>%
  mutate(text = str_replace_all(text, "https://t.co/[A-Za-z\\d]+|&amp;", "")) %>%
  unnest_tokens(word, text, token = "regex", pattern = reg) %>%
  filter(!word %in% stop_words$word,
         str_detect(word, "[a-z]"))

##corupus temızleme
mycorpus <- VCorpus(VectorSource(tweets$text))

removeURL <- function(x) gsub("http[[:alnum:]]*","",x)
removeNumPunct <- function(x) gsub("[^[:alpha:][:space:]]*","",x)

Istenmeyen Kelimeleri Cikaralim

new_stop <- c(stopwords("en"),"rt","one","news")
clean_tweets <- tm_map(mycorpus,PlainTextDocument)
clean_tweets <- tm_map(clean_tweets,content_transformer(removeURL))
clean_tweets <- tm_map(clean_tweets, stripWhitespace)
clean_tweets <- tm_map(clean_tweets, content_transformer(tolower))
clean_tweets <- tm_map(clean_tweets, removeWords, new_stop)
clean_tweets <- tm_map(clean_tweets,content_transformer(removeNumPunct))
clean_tweets <- tm_map(clean_tweets, removePunctuation)

dtm = DocumentTermMatrix(mycorpus)
dtm = removeSparseTerms(dtm, 0.999)
dataset = as.matrix(dtm)
v = sort(colSums(dataset),decreasing=TRUE)
myNames = names(v)
d = data.frame(word=myNames,freq=v)

wordcloud(d$word,d$freq,min.freq = 1,max.words=200,random.order=FALSE, rot.per=0.35,colors=brewer.pal(6, "Dark2"))
